name: Tulip
des: Tulips are erect flowers with long, broad, parallel-veined leaves and a cup-shaped, single or double flower at the tip of the stem.

name: Rose
des: Rose flowers vary in size and shape. They burst with colours ranging from pastel pink, peach, and cream, to vibrant red, yellow and orange

name: Sakura
des: Sakura is the Japanese term for cherry blossom trees. Cherry blossom trees are different from other cherry trees.

name: Golden Retriever
des: The Golden Retriever is a sturdy, muscular dog of medium size, famous for the dense, lustrous coat of gold that gives the breed its name.

name: Chihuahua
des: The Chihuahua is a balanced, graceful dog of terrier-like demeanor, weighing no more than 6 pounds.

name: Akita
des: The Akita is a muscular, double-coated dog of ancient Japanese lineage famous for their dignity, courage, and loyalty.

name: Abyssinian
des: Lithe and long, with a lean, muscular build and moderately wedge-shaped head and large, almond shaped eyes, the Abyssinian is a supermodel of a cat.
